{"tid":1245391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歷史的教訓 和理非/勇武","createTime":"2019-06-20T09:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T09:49:09.000Z","uid":249965,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"81372010e2fe645c235b57d5cce7452634bda0d8","tid":1245391,"uid":249965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:29:18.000Z","msg":"馬丁路德金 （黑人領袖）<br />\n抗爭方法：主張以非暴力的公民抗命<br />\n被搶殺<br />\n<br />\n納爾遜曼德拉 （第一任南非總統）<br />\n抗爭方法：非暴力不服從運動<br />\n被監禁<br />\n<br />\n昂山素姬<br />\n抗爭方法：以便倫魅力呼籲和平集會<br />\n父親被搶殺 昂山素姬被軟禁<br />\n<br />\n結論：<br />\n抗爭者有犧牲自己的準備 監禁/暗殺<br />\n和平方式取得認同<br />\n得到大多數人的憐憫<br />\n<br />\n鼓勵衝的人有冇理解歷史？<br />\n要贏只可以用可憐的方式達致大多數人的憐憫<br />\n612成功係因為黑警使用過份武力並不是武力本身<br />\n我唔係完全不認同武力但只是：<br />\nKill one man, and you are a murderer. Kill millions of men, and you are a conqueror. Kill them all, and you are a god. -Jean Rostand (1939)<br />\n<br />\n明天冇會開又何必武力？"},{"pid":"c416cdd0d70ff27a43c433d8d9bf6fe2a17b28f4","tid":1245391,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1fd09f9e2ad86bc2375a1daf8278621b82d6d7","tid":1245391,"uid":164050,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:33:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3972c68f2cef5197b0d0f8be66bc1fdd1be4ab49","tid":1245391,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:39:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>[全力推] 621 CONTENT PAGE 唔好再俾膠鋪上熱門！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1245051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1245051</a><br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3c4ec4ebc0e39a7575301cc6fe22991e08083241","tid":1245391,"uid":265881,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:40:41.000Z","msg":"成王敗寇 你贏既話 暴動都可以拎大紫荊勳章<img src=\"/assets/faces/d